import { Box, Button, TextField } from "@material-ui/core";
import { AuthenticationContext } from "../../../AuthenticationProvider";

const Profile = () => {
  const valueOf = useContext(AuthenticationContext);
  console.log(valueOf);

  return (
    <Box m={5}>
      <TextField
        autoFocus
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        label="Name"
        type="text"
        fullWidth
      />
      <TextField
        autoFocus
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        label="Email Address"
        type="text"
        fullWidth

        variant="outlined"

        fullWidth

      <Button color="primary" variant="contained">
        Update

};

export default Profile;
